{"type": "article", "id": 49759, "title": "这个意在优化工作效率的工作桌，也能收纳文具小物｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-30T23:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 47432, "name": "Manér Studio"}, {"id": 29767, "name": "LE KLINT"}, {"id": 47433, "name": "Vank"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}, {"id": 47434, "name": "Alessandro Criscito"}, {"id": 18525, "name": "Adam Nathaniel Furman"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 161, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180130235945GA3aVosMnRh86Qmc.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Nakano Twins by Adam Nathaniel Furman</h3><p>伦敦设计师 Adam Nathaniel Furman 创造了一组造型华丽的橱柜 Nakano Twins，模仿了日本 1960 年代购物中心里色彩斑斓的动漫店的形式，色彩对比冲突且鲜明，以及大胆的几何形式，是这组橱柜最显著的特点。Nakano Twins 由粉末涂层钢材制成，底部安装有脚轮，可以承担多种功能。</p><p>按照设计师的说法，他想把这组柜子设计得如同卡通人物一样充满个性，就像是一个喧闹的蹒跚学步的小朋友。在家中，Nakano Twins 可以是饮料酒水台、床头柜、办公室收纳柜等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000013VCLdoqJE314nNiTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000013GFAHTY2bEZNBktL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.536379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018013100001353FgynsWLh6mZNTr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000015v5U9TQMn7VheA6N0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000015h74xpXAfoy3Ycdl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684010\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310000176igWv7OeRyAMUNLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Vank Wall Boxes by Vank</h3><p>开放式办公空间流行了已经有一阵子。家居品牌 Vank 最近推出了一系列隔音吊舱，可以置入任何工作空间使用，既可以用于举办小型会议或视频会议，也可以用作电话间，以及想要从杂乱的工作区中暂时逃离出来的“避风港”。</p><p>每个“吊舱”都覆盖有钻石图案的吸音织物表面，提供高达 45 分贝的保护，门也由高品质的隔热玻璃制成，进一步帮助隔音。“吊舱”提供四种尺寸：单人、双人、三人、四至六人，每一个都配备了 LED 照明，由运动传感器控制的通风系统，以及可适应各种需求的媒体端口。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000145DCyPqnSdEVweAWht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000146xEa7ZbJSiRrwh9UV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310001464w09LubinkeKq8cB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000147jnRYpKt54bA8JOxL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000149GBmnozjHPZg1W6pK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000150BO6iZG1fmeVK2hkc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ARC Lighting Collection by Manér Studio </h3><p>2016 年，丹麦设计师 Nanna Neergaard 和 Marie Hesseldahl 在毕业前夕组建了设计工作室 Manér Studio。他们为丹麦公司 LE KLINT 设计的照明系列 ARC 同时也是其硕士项目，庆祝 LE KLINT 成立 75 周年。</p><p>两人参考了品牌的传统打褶技术，以哥本哈根 Grundtvig 教堂为灵感，借用了其充满曲线的建筑线条和拱门样式，设计了 ARC 系列，包括一个吊灯、台灯、壁灯和落地灯，每个都是黑白色调和橡木的组合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310003109XLUq0taPsS1j6E5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000309eFVsb8nkaurgqH4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310003105GEq4tdPBUegHvZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000311SXrJYbz5Cu3qTBtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000311zCxksionpXlVPWSD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000312Ma84CtOH3NuBrc05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000314FspeklXDzH2Jg8Uo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Enigma: A Foam Cabinet by Alessandro Criscito</h3><p>圣地亚哥工业设计师 Alessandro Criscito 设计了一款名为 Enigma 的“橱柜”，准确来说，它是一个隐藏式书架。设计师在柜架中插入了很多低密度的粉红色泡沫层。Enigma 的结构是开放的，没有柜门，这种设计允许用户的书和其他较为扁平的物体“隐藏收纳”，如果你愿意，也可以选择让书本的部分伸出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018013100033317n5L4tjVdOqfXaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000335TQCG2arIp7cfzqK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.258594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000335GTLORWatESX1hvl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000335XNETVyZiFt9LUbPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000333fDLU6EnNe3kJHmBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pure Desk by 蔡烈超</h3><p>杭州设计师蔡烈超为原创家居设计品牌造作设计了井然工作桌™，是一款专业级工作桌设计，收纳袋、书箱、抽屉、插排盒，4 种功能型收纳模块，优化工作效率。</p><p>井字形木腿，取意井字象形设计。实木质感储物抽屉，将各种文件资料整洁收纳，抽屉内外均以白蜡木实木质感呈现。可拆卸金属书箱，固定于桌面右侧，为工作桌扩容，常用书刊触手可得。11 个超纤皮收纳袋，用于规整文具小物。售价 3800 元起，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300251\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000407m1vk6x3rcsbS02QA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000407nYtUsLNuMy2jRSBK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310004083ZPpGi6STDkhIEnt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000408fqSD0Mk2vpRrUzan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000408yKm3EoL8QZFJtAGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Toucan Decoration by 造作</h3><p>宽大的鸟喙，绚丽的羽毛是犀鸟最被人熟知的特征，设计师从这些特征中汲取灵感，抽象出一只只可爱憨萌的形象，做成实木摆件，用热带雨林独有的生机和活力给你的新年送出第一声问候。珊瑚红与海蓝，意在碰撞出热带丛林的风格，搭配昂首外形。半开放哑光漆，将细腻的木质纹路保留。纤细的腿部造型也撑起挺拔身姿。售价 299 元，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300250\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000511KUkAX5FGZm0tRhzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000438KzDYGXSeRpUIs6iQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000439gSK7yqAvXs2PweLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801310004398FQprJBbv2GVmAoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180131000440SO3latGj6kKhQPNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}